name: Mt Vista
description: Wide open with groups of tall evergreen trees. Great for wings and long range testing.

name: TAI
description: Secluded office park with multiple parking garages and a huge red art sculpture. Great for freestyle.

name: Three Bridges
description: Sprawling office park named for three walking bridges. Lots of gaps and obstacles.

name: Sparks
description: Office park with a secluded courtyard, a large pond, and a tall clock tower. A premier freestyle spot with lots of gaps and obstacles.
